<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Enquiry Received</title>
    <style>
        /* Base styles for email clients */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fdf8ec; /* Matches your LIGHT constant */
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }
        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            table-layout: fixed;
            background-color: #fdf8ec;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .main {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            border-spacing: 0;
            color: #444444;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .header-bar {
            height: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #BFA13B, #8e7421, #BFA13B);
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .ornament {
            margin: 20px auto;
            width: 80px;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: #BFA13B;
            opacity: 0.4;
        }
        h1 {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            color: #1c1917;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #57534e;
        }
        .details-box {
            background-color: #fdf8ec;
            border: 1px solid #e7e5e4;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .detail-item {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .label {
            color: #BFA13B;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #a8a29e;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <center class="wrapper">
        <table class="main" width="100%">
            <tr><td class="header-bar"></td></tr>
            
            <tr>
                <td class="content">
                    <h1>Thank You</h1>
                    <div class="ornament"></div>
                    
                    <p>Dear <strong><%= data.name %></strong>,</p>
                    <p>We have successfully received your enquiry. Our concierge team has been notified and is currently reviewing your request.</p>
                    
                    <div class="details-box">
                        <div class="detail-item">
                            <span class="label">Reference Name:</span><br>
                            <%= data.name %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-item">
                            <span class="label">Your Message:</span><br>
                            <i style="color: #78716c;">"<%= data.query %>"</i>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p>A specialist will reach out to you shortly via <strong><%= data.phone %></strong> to discuss the next steps.</p>
                    
                    <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-style: italic; color: #8e7421;">
                        Refined service, tailored for you.
                    </p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            
            <tr>
                <td class="footer">
                    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Luxury Concierge Team
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </center>
</body>
</html>